# Biome editing

- Read `docs/agents/BIOMES.md` before editing.
- One profile = one file under `src/world/profiles/`.
- Scatter `byBiome()` arrays must have **10** entries (Biome.COUNT).
- `biomeTex.r` stores `biomeId / 16` (see `BIOME_TEX_SCALE`).
- After visual changes: `npm run shoot -- --profile <name> --preset low --seed 1 --out shots/<name>.png`
